<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f6f8;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #1a73e8;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      font-size: 16px;
      background-color: #1a73e8;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
  <title>Welcome Email</title>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Welcome, <%= name %>!</h1>
    <p>We’re excited to have you on board with <strong>OurApp</strong>.</p>
    <p>To get started, please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
    <a href="<%= confirmation_url %>" class="button">Verify Email</a>
    <p>If the button above does not work, copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
    <p><a href="<%= confirmation_url %>"><%= confirmation_url %></a></p>
    <p>Need help? Reply to this email and we’ll assist you right away.</p>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; 2025 OurApp. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
